      <steps class="- topic/ol task/steps ">
         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Connect the serial port on your laptop to the service port
on the HMI module (J405) if the HMI module needs service, and to the
service port on the controller box (J223) if the power module needs
service.</cmd>
