               <note class="- topic/note ">Use the service port cable 940–0024D for the
proper connection of all required signals. If you don’t have
a serial port on your laptop, you can use a USB-to-serial adaptor.
The recommended USB-to-serial adaptors can be found in Service View
or by contacting the technical support.</note>
